<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to My Blog</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* Main Section */
        main {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .intro h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .intro p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .feature {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem;
            width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .features {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .feature {
                width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1>
        <p>Your daily dose of knowledge and inspiration</p>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <h2>About This Blog</h2>
            <p>
                This blog is a platform where I share my thoughts, ideas, and experiences on various topics.
                From technology and programming to lifestyle and personal growth, you'll find a variety of content
                to keep you informed and inspired.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Tech Insights</h3>
                <p>Stay updated with the latest trends and insights in the world of technology and programming.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Personal Growth</h3>
                <p>Explore tips and strategies to improve your productivity, mindset, and overall well-being.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Community</h3>
                <p>Join a community of like-minded individuals who are passionate about learning and growth.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 My Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>